data.description: Exquisite 4-Bedroom Home with Split Floorplan and Stunning Features  Welcome to your dream home! This immaculate 4-bedroom residence, nestled in the heart of a highly sought-after community, offers a perfect blend of space, style, and comfort. With a thoughtfully designed split floorplan, spacious living areas, and charming outdoor spaces, this property is truly a gem.  Key Features:  1. Open Concept Living Space: As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the inviting open floorplan. The large kitchen and dining area seamlessly flow into the living room, creating a perfect space for entertaining family and friends. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace, making it the ideal spot to relax and unwind.  2. Elegant Hardwood Floors: Hardwood floors throughout the main living area not only add warmth but also make maintenance a breeze. They create a timeless and classic ambiance that complements any decor.  3. Sunlit 12x12 Sunroom: Imagine sipping your morning coffee in the delightful 12x12 sunroom, drenched in natural light. Equipped with plantation shutters, this space offers privacy and tranquility, making it perfect for relaxation or as a versatile bonus room.  4. Master Bedroom Oasis: The master bedroom is a true retreat. French doors lead you to a 12x12 covered patio, where you can enjoy the serenity of your spacious backyard. Inside, the master suite includes a full ensuite bathroom with a separate shower and a luxurious jetted tub for unwinding after a long day.  5. Outdoor Paradise: Sitting on a generous .57-acre lot, this property is fully enclosed with a privacy fence, ensuring a secluded and secure environment for your loved ones and pets. The outdoor space also offers plenty of room for gardening, recreation, or even a future pool.  6. Desirable School District: This home is located within the highly regarded District 2 school zone, making it an ideal choice for families looking for top-notch education options for their children.  This exceptional property combines modern living with classic charm, offering an unmatched lifestyle experience. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a showing today and discover the endless possibilities that await you in this remarkable property! Open house on Sunday 10/1 2-4
